{"code":200,"message":"","data":{"id":"10053","movieId":"53","title":"三国的世界","tag":"纪录片","desc":"通过讲述“三国”和其中人物的命运故事，传递他们所承载的传续千年的精神力量和文化底蕴，并探寻那段历史中最有价值的精神本源以及它对后世的深刻影响。","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/three-countries.jpg","introduces":[{"type":1000,"text":"通过讲述“三国”和其中人物的命运故事，传递他们所承载的传续千年的精神力量和文化底蕴，并探寻那段历史中最有价值的精神本源以及它对后世的深刻影响。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/three-countries01.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"《三国的世界》共分为六集，每集50分钟，分别为《良史演义共三国》《星落秋风五丈原》《横槊悲歌观沧海》《义薄云天垂九州》《一江南北真豪杰》《大江东去意未销》。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/three-countries02.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"第一集的主要人物是《三国志》的作者陈寿和《三国演义》的作者罗贯中，以及为《三国志》作注的作者裴松之；第二集的主要人物是蜀相诸葛亮。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"第三集的主要人物是魏武帝曹操；第四集的主要人物是汉寿亭侯关羽。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"第五集是群像，以东吴的孙权、周瑜和鲁肃为主要人物；第六集聚焦三国文化的影响力为何如此普遍、持久。","image":""}],"videos":[{"id":"5114","title":"1、1. 大江东去意未销","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/three-countries.jpg","playCount":"6","playNumber":1,"playNumberDesc":"第一集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d27564550\u0026page\u003d1","m3u8Url":""},{"id":"5115","title":"2、2. 星落秋风五丈原","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/three-countries.jpg","playCount":"6","playNumber":2,"playNumberDesc":"第二集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d27564550\u0026page\u003d2","m3u8Url":""},{"id":"5116","title":"3、3. 横槊悲歌观沧海","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/three-countries.jpg","playCount":"6","playNumber":3,"playNumberDesc":"第三集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d27564550\u0026page\u003d3","m3u8Url":""},{"id":"5117","title":"4、4. 义薄云天垂九州","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master